headline: Gimme Credit Report Warns of Mounting Headwinds for U.S. Health Insurers Amid Regulatory Scrutiny and Funding Challenges
summary: A new report from Gimme Credit's Senior Bond Analyst, Terri Cancelarich highlights growing pressures facing U.S. health insurers amid regulatory scrutiny and funding risks across Medicare Advantage (MA), Medicaid, and ACA exchange programs.
